    "We propose to evaluate the generated molecules from mainly three perspectives: molecular geometry, molecular property distribution and the binding mode within the pocket.",
    "Molecular geometry.",
    "The bond length distribution of the generated molecules was assessed using a methodology similar to the one used in the TargetDiff study.",
    "Specifically, around 10,000 molecules were generated for each of the three models tested in the study.",
    "These molecules were generated for 100 targets in the CrossDocked2020 dataset."
